Avusa Agrees to Four-Week Due Diligence By Capitau Group After Offer

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-16T15:08:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-16/avusa-agrees-to-four-week-due-diligence-by-capitau-group-after-offer.html
Avusa Ltd. (AVU)  said it agreed to let a
group led by Capitau Holdings Ltd. undertake a four-week due
diligence of the company after it made a take over offer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
